  <brief_title>Blown Nasal Secretion Measurements in Rhinosinusitis: Repeatability and Validity Compared to Nasal Lavage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Repeatability and Validity of Measurements in Blown Nasal Secretion in Patients With Rhinosinusitis</official_title>
