  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To process blown nasal secretions from subjects with rhinosinusitis and to obtain a specimen
      by nasal lavage. To investigate the reliability and validity of the measurements we will
      determine their repeatability and compare them with those of nasal lavage in the same
      subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
